Slapd - standalong ldapd dameon. it listen for all LDAP connection at port 389, and respond to all ldap operations it receives
from client.
all configuration can be done in slapd, this helps to dynamically manange ldap configruation, so no need to restart service
on every change in configuration file.
ldap-utils - it provides all necessry package to ldap server.
#sudo apt-get install slapd ldap-utils







Ldap web interface setup:- 
LDAP GUI:- used to maintain directory structe in ldap
gui used - phpldapadmin; apache directory studio
apache directory studio:- can be download from directory.apache.org


